OL,3,CNI consultant doctors to be best paid
OL,4,Cin UK after pay deal
OL,6,FConsultant doctors who are members of
OL,7,Fthe British Medical Association in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland have voted to accept
OL,9,Fa pay offer from Stormont's Department
OL,10,Fof Health.
OL,12,FOver 94% of consultants voted to
OL,13,Faccept an average uplift of 5.26%.
OL,15,FThe uplift is in addition to the 6%
OL,16,Falready awarded in the 2023/24 pay
OL,17,Freview and is separate to any
OL,18,Fsubsequent pay award in 24/25.
OL,20,FConsultants in NI will now have the
OL,21,Fhighest starting salary in the UK.
