OL,3,CNI consultant doctors to be best paid
OL,4,Cin UK after pay deal
OL,6,F"It means that doctors will not be
OL,7,Fleaving Northern Ireland for financial
OL,8,Freasons to go elsewhere in the UK,"
OL,9,Fsaid Dr David Farren, chair of BMA in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,F"We are no longer on the back foot
OL,13,Fwhen it comes to UK nations, we are
OL,14,Ffirmly in the middle.
