OL,3,CNI consultant doctors to be best paid
OL,4,Cin UK after pay deal
OL,6,F"Salaries still are higher in the
OL,7,FRepublic of Ireland, for example and
OL,8,Felsewhere across the world, people
OL,9,Fwill have their own reasons for moving
OL,10,Fbut what this does is make it less
OL,11,Flikely, it increases the friction for
OL,12,Fpeople who are considering moving for
OL,13,Ffinancial reasons."
OL,15,FAlthough the dispute may have ended
OL,16,Ffor consultants, it's a different
OL,17,Fstory for junior doctors.
